    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.5,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.5,
      "end": 3.52,
      "text": "6월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 3.52,
      "end": 4.56,
      "text": "Little Italy"
    },
    {
      "start": 4.56,
      "end": 6.78,
      "text": "It's about Nikki and Leo"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.78,
      "end": 9.98,
      "text": "who are staunch competitors and best friends"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.98,
      "end": 13.7,
      "text": "growing up in the Little Italy neighborhood of Toronto, Canada"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.7,
      "end": 15.8,
      "text": "오! 어서 오십시오!"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.34,
      "end": 18.54,
      "text": "Welcome! Good to be here! Good morning!"
    },
    {
      "start": 18.76,
      "end": 24.92,
      "text": "네, 이렇게 양가의 그런 경쟁 구도에 대해서도 살짝 언급을 해주셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.92,
      "end": 27.38,
      "text": "It's a family war! A pizza war!"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.74,
      "end": 30.34,
      "text": "이 도널드 감독이요"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.34,
      "end": 35.68,
      "text": "He's known as rom-com 장인이다 라고도 말씀을 드렸었잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 35.68,
      "end": 37.34,
      "text": "The master of rom-coms."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.34,
      "end": 40.8,
      "text": "네, 그만큼 이 캐스팅에도 완벽을 기한 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 41.26,
      "end": 41.56,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.84,
      "end": 43.84,
      "text": "Yeah, it was, as we said, the couple"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.84,
      "end": 46.32,
      "text": "리키, 니키, 리키 아니고"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.32,
      "end": 49.12,
      "text": "니키 and Leo are a match made in heaven"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.12,
      "end": 52.82,
      "text": "and they actually, they wanted to work with each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.32,
      "end": 56.6,
      "text": "So Donald, he was casting for the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.6,
      "end": 59.48,
      "text": "and at first nobody, when he got the project"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.48,
      "end": 61.68,
      "text": "이 마켓을 때, 배우 아무도 없어가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.68,
      "end": 65.14,
      "text": "He said, oh, we heard that Emma was interested"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.14,
      "end": 67.94,
      "text": "Emma, Emma Roberts"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.94,
      "end": 70.86,
      "text": "and that she wanted to work with Hayden"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.86,
      "end": 74.0,
      "text": "So she personally wanted to work with this guy"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.0,
      "end": 78.9,
      "text": "그래서 이 감독님은 respected her opinion 한 거고"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.9,
      "end": 81.76,
      "text": "결국, as she said, 말한 것처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.76,
      "end": 83.7,
      "text": "he cast him, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.86,
      "end": 86.1,
      "text": "Yes, which is a bit surprising"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.1,
      "end": 87.38,
      "text": "because when you think of Hayden"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.38,
      "end": 91.02,
      "text": "I mentioned he played Darth Vader and Luke Skywalker"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.02,
      "end": 93.74,
      "text": "two roles in the same movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.74,
      "end": 96.0,
      "text": "and he's known for dark, serious roles"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.0,
      "end": 97.48,
      "text": "but this is a rom-com"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.48,
      "end": 99.68,
      "text": "totally different from his usual thing"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.68,
      "end": 103.06,
      "text": "so as a director, you might not want to cast him"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.06,
      "end": 104.5,
      "text": "but he did"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.5,
      "end": 106.76,
      "text": "and Hayden actually loved it"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.76,
      "end": 109.6,
      "text": "He said that he smiled more in this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.6,
      "end": 111.86,
      "text": "than he smiled in his whole career"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.86,
      "end": 113.92,
      "text": "His career sounds pretty sad"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.92,
      "end": 115.46,
      "text": "if he didn't smile that much"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.46,
      "end": 116.3,
      "text": "그렇군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.3,
      "end": 119.82,
      "text": "여태까지 맡았던 역할들이 대부분 다 어둡고"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.82,
      "end": 122.8,
      "text": "무겁고 이런 역할을 했었기 때문에"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.8,
      "end": 126.42,
      "text": "과연 Hayden이 잘 해낼까라고 의구심도 들었겠지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.42,
      "end": 128.86,
      "text": "이 Hayden이 너무너무 잘해줬죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.86,
      "end": 131.52,
      "text": "그리고 너무너무 개인적으로도"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.52,
      "end": 134.8,
      "text": "많이 웃었던 영화였다라고 이야기를 했다고 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.8,
      "end": 135.86,
      "text": "그동안 참았나봐요"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.86,
      "end": 137.86,
      "text": "집에서만 멀어서 웃었나봐요"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.86,
      "end": 139.56,
      "text": "이럴 때 막 진지하게 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.56,
      "end": 140.8,
      "text": "그럴 수도 있고"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.8,
      "end": 143.0,
      "text": "I thought they really liked each other"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.0,
      "end": 143.88,
      "text": "어쩌면"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.88,
      "end": 144.88,
      "text": "That's what I thought"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.88,
      "end": 146.92,
      "text": "They may have dated in real life, too"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.92,
      "end": 149.32,
      "text": "그랬으면 좋겠다라는 생각까지 했어요, 사실은"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.32,
      "end": 149.66,
      "text": "Oh, really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.8,
      "end": 152.0,
      "text": "네, 굉장히 이 입을 해서 봤죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.0,
      "end": 153.1,
      "text": "순수하게 사귀었으면"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.1,
      "end": 157.26,
      "text": "거의 그런 느낌의 케미스트리를 느낄 수가 있었습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.26,
      "end": 159.38,
      "text": "그럼 오늘 장면 듣고 오시죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.38,
      "end": 161.4,
      "text": "You scared me to death"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.4,
      "end": 162.96,
      "text": "What's going on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.38,
      "end": 164.5,
      "text": "What you doing here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.36,
      "end": 170.82,
      "text": "Now it's bad luck to be superstitious"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.82,
      "end": 172.1,
      "text": "Franca"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.1,
      "end": 174.97,
      "text": "With the Virgin Mary as my witness"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.97,
      "end": 176.31,
      "text": "Will you marry me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.03,
      "end": 177.31,
